description: send HEAD requests to proxy of Service

parameters.description: Path is the part of URLs that include service endpoints, suffixes, and parameters to use for the current proxy request to service. For example, the whole request URL is `http://localhost/api/v1/namespaces/kube-system/services/elasticsearch-logging/_search?q=user:kimchy`. Path is `_search?q=user:kimchy`.
parameters.name: path
